[[File:Iccc wiki.jpg|thumb|International Chamber Choir Competition, 2005.]]
The '''International Chamber Choir Competition Marktoberdorf''' is a competition for [[chamber choir]]s held every two years in [[Marktoberdorf]], near [[Munich]] in southern [[Germany]].<ref name="chorverbaende">{{cite web| url=http://www.chorverbaende.de/en/modfestivals/international-chamber-choir-competition-marktoberdorf.html | title=International Chamber Choir Competition Marktoberdorf | publisher=Bundesvereinigung Deutscher Chorverbände e.V.] | location=Germany | accessdate=5 September 2015 }}</ref>
Founded in 1989, the 14th competition was held 22–27 May 2015.<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.choralnet.org/view/445856 | title=14th International Chamber Choir Competition Marktoberdorf | publisher= ChoralNet | accessdate=5 September 2015 }}</ref> In the first 13 competitions, nearly 200 choirs from more than 40 countries have participated.<ref name="chorverbaende" />
